item.title: CVE-2019-9505|2024-08-04T21:54:44.054Z -- printerlogic -- management%20software
item.description: The PrinterLogic Print Management software, versions up to and including 18.3.1.96, does not sanitize special characters allowing for remote unauthorized changes to configuration files. An unauthenticated attacker may be able to remotely execute arbitrary code with SYSTEM privileges.
